Step 4

on va maintenant crÃ©er notre cluster kubernetes 

gcloud container clusters create ${CLUSTER} \
    --project=${PROJET} \
    --zone=${ZONE} \
    --scopes "https://www.googleapis.com/auth/projecthosting,storage-rw"

on recupere le PROJECT_NUMBER
export PROJECT_NUMBER="$(gcloud projects describe \
    $(gcloud config get-value core/project -q) --format='get(projectNumber)')"

	ajouter le role developeur kubernetes a cloud build
gcloud projects add-iam-policy-binding ${PROJET} \
    --member=serviceAccount:${PROJECT_NUMBER}@cloudbuild.gserviceaccount.com \
    --role=roles/container.developer
Your environment is ready!


